snippet.title: Wildmender - Official Demo Trailer | Future of Play Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Explore the world of Wildmender in this trailer for the desert gardening survival game. Wildmender will be available on Steam, Xbox Series X/S, and PlayStation 5, and a demo will be available for Wildmender as part of Steam Next Fest this June. In Wildmender, start from a tiny spring and cultivate a blooming garden. Explore a vast world amid the sands and uncover its mysteries.

#GameTrailers #SummerOfGaming
